<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.8.4">
<l>nāṟiya cāntam namakkiṟai nalkeṉṉat</l>
<l>tēṟi yavaḷun tiruvuṭam piṟpūca</l>
<l>vūṟiya kūṉiṉai yuḷḷē yoṭuṅkavaṉ</l>
<l>ṟēṟa vuruviṉā yaccōvaccō</l>
<l rend="indent">vemperu māṉvārā vaccōvaccō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who pierced [her] oozing hump that day</l>
<l>so that [it] shrunk inside [and she] rose up,</l>
<l>when [you] said, “give a little fragrant sandal to us,”</l>
<l>having understood, she annointed [your] holy body!</l>
<l rend="indent">Oh! Oh! our Lord has come, Oh! Oh!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
